<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4690749>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Dorsal and lateral views of the lectotype of Calligrapha serpentina (Rogers) (a), lectotype of C. mexicana Stål (b), lectotype of C. serpentina var. discrepans (Achard) (c), holotype of C. serpentina ssp. temaxensis Bechyné (d), holotype of C. sallei (Achard) (e), and lectotype of C. serpens Bowditch (f). Scale = 5.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4690749/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4690751>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Dorsal (apex), ventral and lateral views of the penises of Calligrapha serpentina (Rogers) (a), C. mexicana Stål (b), C. sallei (Achard) (c), C. discrepans (Achard) (d), and C. serpentina ssp. temaxensis Bechyné (e). Scale = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4690751/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4690753>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Distribution of Calligrapha serpentina (Rogers) (white circles) and of C. mexicana Stål (black circles)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4690753/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

